title: #92Noon! Full show from Zimmer's Kentucky Ranch!
description: Awesome show with PA & Wobby from Northern Kentucky, home of Vikings head coach Mike Zimmer's ranch. Guests include Bengals coach Marvin Lewis, Vikings TE Kyle Rudolph, Zimmer's mom Ann, Zimmer's son & LB coach Adam and career Cowboys safety Darren Woodson!
